ight-aero-carbon-handlebar_more-rapid_less-weight_photo-by-Chris-Auld_DePanne-win-630x420.jpg 630w\"></a></p><p>Roval vaguely claims that their Win Tunnel work saves 20 seconds over a conventional round bar in the course of a road race, without any more detail. They did work with the pros of Deceuninck–Quick-Step though to settle on the shape &amp; ergonomics of the new Rapide bar. And that seems to have delivered solid results already. Together Mark Cavendish and Sam Bennett have already chalked up ten individual stage race wins this season on the new bar.<span data-ez-name=\"bikerumor_com-medrectangle-3\"></span></p><h3>Tech details</h3><p><a href=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/05/24074900/Roval-Rapide-lightweight-aero-carbon-handlebar_more-rapid_less-weight_top-studio.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/05/24074900/Roval-Rapide-lightweight-aero-carbon-handlebar_more-rapid_less-weight_top-studio.jpg\" alt=\"Roval Rapide lightweight aero carbon handlebar, more rapid, less weight, studio top\" width=\"2000\" height=\"800\" data-ezsrcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/05/24074900/Roval-Rapide-lightweight-aero-carbon-handlebar_more-rapid_less-weight_top-studio.jpg 2000w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/05/24074900/Roval-Rapide-lightweight-aero-carbon-handlebar_more-rapid_less-weight_top-studio-297x119.jpg 297w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/05/24074900/Roval-Rapide-lightweight-aero-carbon-handlebar_more-rapid_less-weight_top-studio-800x320.jpg 800w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/05/24074900/Roval-Rapide-lightweight-aero-carbon-handlebar_more-rapid_less-weight_top-studio-120x48.jpg 120w,https://bikerumor.com/