pide-lightweight-aero-carbon-handlebar_more-rapid_less-weight_top-studio-800x320.jpg 800w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/05/24074900/Roval-Rapide-lightweight-aero-carbon-handlebar_more-rapid_less-weight_top-studio-120x48.jpg 120w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/05/24074900/Roval-Rapide-lightweight-aero-carbon-handlebar_more-rapid_less-weight_top-studio-768x307.jpg 768w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/05/24074900/Roval-Rapide-lightweight-aero-carbon-handlebar_more-rapid_less-weight_top-studio-1536x614.jpg 1536w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/05/24074900/Roval-Rapide-lightweight-aero-carbon-handlebar_more-rapid_less-weight_top-studio-696x278.jpg 696w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/05/24074900/Roval-Rapide-lightweight-aero-carbon-handlebar_more-rapid_less-weight_top-studio-1068x427.jpg 1068w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/05/24074900/Roval-Rapide-lightweight-aero-carbon-handlebar_more-rapid_less-weight_top-studio-1920x768.jpg 1920w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/05/24074900/Roval-Rapide-lightweight-aero-carbon-handlebar_more-rapid_less-weight_top-studio-1050x420.jpg 1050w\"></a></p><p>The aero tops of the bar sweep slightly forward to allow more space for the rider’s arms &amp; legs in the sprint. The carbon tops also feature a unique textured surface for grip even when wet without bar tape. There’s also a molded-in step to the bar just after the bend for a flush finish to your wrap job &amp; smooth transition from tape to the unwrapped tops, plus full internal cable routing &amp; Di2 junction box compatibility.</p><p><a href=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bi